high_descs: Go around the kitchen island on the left hand side and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug that is sitting on the coffee maker.
Step to the right and face the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink then take it out.
Step to the left and face the coffee maker.
Place the mug back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Wash a mug and place in coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the oven, then hang a left and walk across the room to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Take the dirty mug out of the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Wash the dirty mug in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the coffee machine.
Put the clean coffee mug into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left, move all the way around the center island to the left, keep going until you get to the coffee machine past the sink on the right.
Pick up the dirty mug on the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the sink to the right.
Wash the mug in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned mug back to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the cleaned mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned mug on the coffee machine.
